{"content_type": "text/html", "site": {"name": "Lux", "date": "2014-10-14T08-24-22", "lux_version": "0.1.0-alpha.1", "media": "/media", "template_engine": null, "template": "doc.html", "year": 2014, "python_version": "3.4.1", "url": "http://quantmind.github.io/lux"}, "head": {}, "html_url": "http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/api/base", "html": {"main": "<section id=\"page-header\" class=\"page-header-outer api_base-header\">\n    <div class=\"layer\">\n        <div class=\"page-header\">\n            <div class=\"container fullpage\">\n                <div class=\"row fullpage\">\n                    <div class=\"col-sm-12 text-center\">\n                        <breadcrumbs></breadcrumbs>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<div id=\"page-main\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"api_base-main col-md-12\">\n                <div class=\"center-block\" style=\"max-width: 900px\" data-highlight data-hash-scroll>\n                    <div class=\"section\" id=\"module-lux.extensions.base\">\n<span id=\"base-extension\"></span><span id=\"middleware-base\"></span><h1>Base Extension<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#module-lux.extensions.base\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>The base <em class=\"xref std std-ref\">lux extension</em> provides several\nmiddleware utilities. If used, it should be the first extension in your\n<tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">EXTENSIONS</span></tt> list (excluding extensions which\ndon&#8217;t provide any wsgi middleware such as <tt class=\"xref py py-mod docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">lux.extensions.sitemap</span></tt>\nfor example).</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"parameters\">\n<h2>Parameters<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#parameters\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"clean-url\">\n<span id=\"std:setting-CLEAN_URL\"></span><h3>CLEAN_URL<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#clean-url\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Default: <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">'False'</span></tt></p>\n<p>When <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">True</span></tt>, requests on url with consecutive slashes are converted to valid url and redirected.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"favicon\">\n<span id=\"std:setting-FAVICON\"></span><h3>FAVICON<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#favicon\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Default: <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">'None'</span></tt></p>\n<p>Adds wsgi middleware to handle favicon url <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">/favicon.ico``served</span> <span class=\"pre\">from</span> <span class=\"pre\">``MEDIA_URL/FAVICON</span></tt></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"gzip-min-length\">\n<span id=\"std:setting-GZIP_MIN_LENGTH\"></span><h3>GZIP_MIN_LENGTH<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#gzip-min-length\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Default: <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">'200'</span></tt></p>\n<p>If a positive integer, a response middleware is added so that it encodes the response via the gzip algorithm.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"serve-static-files\">\n<span id=\"std:setting-SERVE_STATIC_FILES\"></span><h3>SERVE_STATIC_FILES<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#serve-static-files\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Default: <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">'False'</span></tt></p>\n<p>if <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">True</span></tt> add middleware to serve static files.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"use-etags\">\n<span id=\"std:setting-USE_ETAGS\"></span><h3>USE_ETAGS<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#use-etags\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Default: <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">'False'</span></tt></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"media-handling\">\n<h2>Media Handling<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#media-handling\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>When the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-SERVE_STATIC_FILES\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">SERVE_STATIC_FILES</span></tt></a> parameter is set to <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">True</span></tt>,\nthis extension adds middleware for serving static files from\n<tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">MEDIA_URL</span></tt>.\nIn addition, a <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"params#std:setting-FAVICON\"><tt class=\"xref std std-setting docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">FAVICON</span></tt></a> location can also be specified.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class='small hidden-print text-muted' id='page-footer'>\n    <div class='container'>\n        <div class='row'>\n            <div class='block col-sm-5'>\n                <div class='hidden-xs'>\n                    <ul class=\"fa-ul text-left\">\n    <li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-copyright\"></i>2014 <a href=\"http://quantmind.com\">Quantmind</a></li>\n    <li>Site build with Lux on python 3.4.1</li>\n    <li>Docs build with <a href=\"http://sphinx-doc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Sphinx</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/changelog\">Changelog</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/api/\">API</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/docs/EXTENSIONS/\">Extensions</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://quantmind.github.io/lux/images\">Images</a></li>\n</ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class='text-center visible-xs'>\n                    <ul class=\"fa-ul text-left\">\n    <li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-co